## Generating a presentation based on brand guide
Step 1: Read CLEARSKY_DESIGN_GUIDE.md for color/font/layout specs
Step 2: Select output type (tearsheet/deck/whitepaper)
Step 3: POST to /api/presentations/v2/generate with prompt + type
Step 4: Parse response JSON into field schema
Step 5: Call buildBuf(brief, imageBase64, imageExt) → ArrayBuffer
Step 6: Download via Blob URL

## pptxgenjs patterns
```javascript
// Setup
const pptx = new PptxGenJS();
pptx.layout = 'LAYOUT_WIDE'; // or 'LAYOUT_A4'
pptx.author = 'ClearSky Limited';

// Slide
const slide = pptx.addSlide();

// Text with brand colors
slide.addText('Title', {
  x: 0.5, y: 0.3, w: 9, h: 0.8,
  fontSize: 32, bold: true,
  color: 'FFFFFF',
  fontFace: 'Georgia'
});

// Colored rectangle
slide.addShape(pptx.ShapeType.rect, {
  x: 0, y: 0, w: 10, h: 5.625,
  fill: { color: '0D1B3E' }
});

// Always use shrinkText:true on text boxes
slide.addText(longText, {
  x: 0.5, y: 1.5, w: 8, h: 2,
  shrinkText: true,
  fontSize: 14,
  color: '2C3E50'
});

// Generate buffer (for download)
const buf = await pptx.write({ outputType: 'arraybuffer' });
```

## AI-optional fallback (Standing Rule #28)
```javascript
async function generateBrief(prompt, type) {
  try {
    const res = await Promise.race([
      fetch(API + '/api/presentations/v2/generate', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: {'Content-Type':'application/json'},
        body: JSON.stringify({prompt, type})
      }),
      new Promise((_,r) => setTimeout(() => r(new Error('timeout')), 30000))
    ]);
    if (!res.ok) throw new Error('API error ' + res.status);
    return await res.json();
  } catch(e) {
    console.warn('AI brief failed, using fallback:', e.message);
    // Degrade to MOCK_PROJECTS or manual input
    showDegradedBanner('AI brief unavailable — fill fields manually or paste text');
    return buildFallbackBrief(prompt, type);
  }
}
```

## URL parameter integration (pending Week 2)
presentations-v3.html will read:
- ?buyer=Shell → pre-populate counterparty field + search wiki for Shell context
- ?project=985 → pre-populate project selector + auto-ingest PD if available
- ?type=tearsheet → pre-select output type

## Gotchas
- pptxgenjs 3.12.0 from cdnjs — do NOT upgrade without testing (breaking API changes)
- shrinkText:true is mandatory — different OS render fonts differently
- Georgia font may not render on all systems — always specify fallback
- Image fetch (line 949) uses generic fetch() for base64 — may fail on CORS
- MOCK_PROJECTS fallback is stale — update when adding new portfolio projects
- Worker endpoint ANTHROPIC_API_KEY must be set via wrangler secret put
